---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Why Choose Shelby Web Company Over the Competition? | Shelby Web Co"
  description="Discover what sets Shelby Web Company apart. We provide professional web design, branding, and SEO tailored for local businesses in Shelby, NC."
>
  <article class="pt-32 pb-24 px-4 bg-[#0A0A0A]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="mb-16 text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-brand-accent/20 bg-brand-accent/5">
          <span class="text-brand-accent text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Our Philosophy</span>
          <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-brand-accent/30"></span>
          <span class="text-brand-sky/60 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest">Vol #1 Article #1 • January 2025</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-8 tracking-tight leading-[1.1]">
          Why Choose <br />
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-cyan to-brand-blue">Shelby Web Company?</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-sky/80 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto italic">
          A Local Partner for High-End Digital Growth
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- Main Image Placeholder -->
      <div class="aspect-video bg-brand-dark border border-white/5 rounded-3xl mb-16 overflow-hidden shadow-2xl relative group">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue/20 to-transparent opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-center">
           <span class="text-brand-sky/20 font-heading text-4xl font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] transform -rotate-12 px-4">The Shelby Web Co. <br/> Difference</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg text-brand-sky/90 mb-12">
          Building strong local businesses starts with a strong online presence. In today's digital-first world, your website and online presence are often the first impression customers have of your business. For local businesses in Shelby, North Carolina and the surrounding areas, choosing the right digital partner can make the difference between being found — or being overlooked.
        </p>

        <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          At <strong>Shelby Web Company</strong>, we don't just build websites. We help local businesses stand out, compete, and grow in an increasingly crowded online marketplace.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-brand-accent">01.</span> We're Local — and That Matters
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-8">
            Unlike large agencies or out-of-town freelancers, we understand the Shelby market. We know how customers search for local services, what local competitors are doing online, and how to optimize for Shelby, Cleveland County, and surrounding areas. Being local means better communication, faster support, and strategies that actually make sense for your community.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-brand-accent">02.</span> Custom Web Design — Not Templates
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-8">
            Your business is unique. Your website should be too. We specialize in custom-designed websites tailored to your brand, mobile-friendly layouts that look great on any device, and clean, modern designs built for speed and usability. We don't rely on cookie-cutter templates that make your business blend in. Instead, we create websites designed to convert visitors into customers.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-brand-accent">03.</span> Branding & Logos That Build Trust
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-8">
            First impressions matter — especially online. Whether you're starting a new business or refreshing an existing brand, we help with professional logo design, brand consistency across your website and online platforms, and visual identity that builds credibility. A strong brand helps customers feel confident choosing you over competitors.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-brand-accent">04.</span> We Care About Your Long-Term Success
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-12">
            Your website isn't a "set it and forget it" project. We work with local businesses to improve and update their site over time, adjust SEO strategies as competition changes, and grow alongside their business goals. When your business succeeds, our reputation grows with it — and that's how we like it.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue/10 to-transparent border border-brand-blue/20 p-8 my-16 rounded-3xl">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">What Sets Us Apart?</h3>
          <ul class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 list-none p-0 m-0">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="text-brand-cyan font-bold">✓</span>
              <span class="text-brand-sky/90"><strong>Local Focus:</strong> Part of the community.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="text-brand-cyan font-bold">✓</span>
              <span class="text-brand-sky/90"><strong>Direct Service:</strong> No outsourcing.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="text-brand-cyan font-bold">✓</span>
              <span class="text-brand-sky/90"><strong>Proven Results:</strong> Track record of growth.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="text-brand-cyan font-bold">✓</span>
              <span class="text-brand-sky/90"><strong>Complete Solutions:</strong> Design, SEO, Branding.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue to-brand-darkest p-12 rounded-[2rem] text-center relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_50%_50%,rgba(0,255,255,0.1),transparent_70%)]"></div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-6 relative z-10 text-center">Ready to Grow Your Local Business?</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-white/80 mb-10 relative z-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Let's talk about how we can help your Shelby business stand out online and attract more local customers.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center relative z-10">
            <a href="/contact" class="bg-white text-brand-darkest px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-brand-sky transition-all">
              Get Free Consultation
            </a>
            <a href="/services" class="bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-md text-white border border-white/20 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-black/30 transition-all">
              View All Services
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-24 p-8 bg-brand-dark/50 border border-white/5 rounded-2xl text-center">
            <p class="text-brand-sky/60 text-sm mb-4">
                This article was written and published by <strong>Shelby Web Company</strong>.
            </p>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/60 text-sm m-0">
                A partner for high-end web design and local SEO in Shelby, NC. Visit <a href="/" class="text-brand-cyan hover:underline">www.shelbywebco.com</a>.
            </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer navigation -->
      <footer class="mt-24 pt-12 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-wrap gap-8 items-center justify-between">
        <a href="/blog" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
          Back to Blog
        </a>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <a href="/" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">Home</a>
          <a href="/about" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">About Us</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">Contact</a>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
